data.description: Are you looking for a place to call your own? This energy-efficient home with OWNED SOLAR, nestled on a desirable corner lot, is now on the market! Upon arrival, you will be greeted by an RV gate and a cozy porch where you can sit and enjoy the peaceful neighborhood. Inside, you'll discover an inviting living room, perfect for relaxing after a long, tiring day. The tile flooring, complemented by a soothing palette, creates a homey interior. Cook your favorite meals in the eat-in kitchen, boasting wood cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Well-appointed and perfectly sized -the bedrooms serve as perfect retreats. The backyard features a covered patio, a storage shed, and a lot of potential to become your own oasis. Don't miss this amazing opportunity! Visit right now
